{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS","iPadOS","Mac Catalyst"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"sections":[],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"case","externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeVertical","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"If a text’s language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"placement would be laid out vertically.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeVertical":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodevertical","abstract":[{"text":"If a text’s language supports vertical writing mode, symbols with point","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"placement would be laid out vertically.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeVertical","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNTextWritingModeVertical"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","abstract":[{"text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","title":"MLNTextWritingMode","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"}}}